-- World Bank Backs $700 Million, Five-Year `Strategic Alliance' With Uruguay
-- B y   B i l l   F a r i e s
-- 2010-10-14T17:01:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-14/world-bank-backs-700-million-five-year-strategic-alliance-with-uruguay.html
The World Bank’s board approved a
$700 million “strategic alliance” with Uruguay for the
2010-2015 period, the Washington-based lender said in an e-
mailed statement.  Uruguay will receive a $100 million loan to improve public
administration and promote economic stability, the statement
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bill Faries at 
 wfaries@bloomberg.net  